&lt;p&gt;An opportunity has arisen for a Senior ED Admin to join the Emergency Department at Wexham Park Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be expected to take on a variety of tasks such as presenting as the on-site lead for admin, and deputising for the lead admin manager in ED working in the new EAC &lt;em&gt;(Emergency&lt;/em&gt; Ambulatory Care), the successful candidate will work within a team to maintain an excellent customer service that supports the NHS and Trust Waiting List targets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Full training will be given to the successful candidate in electronic systems such as the Patient Management System (Symphony). This post is an excellent opportunity to develop skills working within the Emergency Department in a band 3 role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This position is based on a shift pattern, example rota attached to vacancy documents.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Previous applicants need not apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Doreen Bader&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lead Administrator&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;07774016579&lt;/p&gt;
